Mario rides on a dangerous, and frankly tedious journey. Why? Why not? - Prod. Code: 8992-077B, Rel. Date: 11/26/22, 10:27pm
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.
Careful, these creepy crawling beetles just love roaming around on all these wooden walkways! think you can find their hidden Tanooki suit though?
